# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  TrackSite Attendance System — Environment Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
#  Copy this file to .env and adjust values for your site.
#
#  Usage:
#    cp .env.example .env
#    nano .env
#

# ── Project / Device ──────────────────────────────────────
# Set PROJECT_ID to filter workers by project assignment.
# Leave as 0 to load ALL active workers (no filter).
PROJECT_ID=1
DEVICE_NAME=Site-Device-01

# ── MySQL Database (Central Server) ──────────────────────
MYSQL_HOST=localhost
MYSQL_PORT=3306
MYSQL_USER=root
MYSQL_PASSWORD=
MYSQL_DATABASE=construction_management

# ── SQLite (Local Buffer) ────────────────────────────────
SQLITE_PATH=data/local.db

# ── Face Recognition ─────────────────────────────────────
# Lower tolerance = stricter matching (default 0.5, range 0.3–0.6)
FACE_TOLERANCE=0.5

# ── Anti-Accidental Safeguards ───────────────────────────
# STABILITY_SECONDS  — Seconds the worker must stay in frame
# COOLDOWN_SECONDS   — Seconds before the same worker can scan again
# MIN_WORK_INTERVAL  — Minimum minutes between Time In and Time Out
STABILITY_SECONDS=3.0
COOLDOWN_SECONDS=60.0
MIN_WORK_INTERVAL=30

# ── Synchronization ─────────────────────────────────────
# SYNC_INTERVAL — Seconds between background sync attempts
# SYNC_API_URL  — HTTP endpoint for remote sync (leave empty for direct MySQL)
# SYNC_API_KEY  — Shared secret for API authentication
SYNC_INTERVAL=300
SYNC_API_URL=
SYNC_API_KEY=

# ── Camera ───────────────────────────────────────────────
CAMERA_INDEX=0

# ── Display ──────────────────────────────────────────────
FULLSCREEN=false
WINDOW_WIDTH=1280
WINDOW_HEIGHT=800

# ── Logging ──────────────────────────────────────────────
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
